comments: Extremely sweet!!! Loved her! She will help you no matter what! She made algebra really easy for me to learn! Made an A in 105 and 106 thanks to her! Highly recommend that you take her if you can!!!
AMAZING TEACHER! HAND DOWNS! she is the best math teacher at UTC. she explains everything if you don\'t understands an loves helping her students. TAKE HER for MATH 105 & 106!

DEFIANTLY TAKE HER! if you struggle in math she is a teacher that makes it crystal clear and she will help you one on one. come to class its a percentage in your grade, take notes, and keep up with online homework and you will do great. she is very helpful in many ways. Defiantly take her, it must do class and teacher.
She\'s an AMAZING teacher. As long as you put forth effort in class and show up to take notes you\'ll do great. Her reviews make the test easy. I highly recommend her if you need a 106 class.

Lucky to have her as my teacher! I always had a hard time with math in the past but she really made everything easier! All of the homework is online which helps when I have a question about a problem, she can usually help through e-mail or in the next class! She\'s such a great teacher that I\'m taking my next level math class from her too!

I think Ms. Angel is a wonderful teacher. Those of you who have a problem with the pace should take a class that meets more often. My work schedule caused me to register for her class. I learned a lot and thought the pace was fine. She is very nice and willing to help as much as she can.

I enjoyed her class, but I had to work REALLY hard! I took the night class. I think this is the only time she teaches. Every nigt she taught two or three sections. If you take her, you have got to stay on top of the online homework and take good notes. If you struggle in math, take the class during the day because the night classes go REALLY fast..
Very confusing teacher. Sometimes she forgot what we were doing in the middle of the lessons and her class was out of control.
She is the BEST math teacher I have ever had! She is easy to understand and breaks down the material so that people can get it. If you can, take her class. You won\'t regret it...
